text: The 14 July Revolution also called the 1958 Iraqi military coup was a coup d'etat that happened during 14 July 1958. This resulted in the murder of Faisal II and the removal of the Hashemite-led Kingdom of Iraq. ==References== Category:1958 in Asia Category:20th century in Iraq Category:Coups d'Ã©tat
